text: Örgryte IS is an association football club which in the town of Gothenburg in Sweden. The club won the first Swedish national championship in 1896, and was one of the stronger teams in Swedish association football of the late 19th century and early 20th century. The club also won the Swedish national championship in 1896, 1897, 1898, 1899, 1902, 1904, 1905, 1906, 1907, 1909, 1913 and 1985 ==References== == Other websites == *Official website Category:Swedish football clubs Category:1887 establishments in Europe Category:Sport in Gothenburg Category:1880s establishments in Sweden
